metadata.name: The Eye Of Life
metadata.description:
An eye that allows you to look into the meaning of life is a metaphorical representation of the search for understanding and purpose. 

This eye symbolizes the journey of self-discovery and personal growth that every individual experiences at some point in their lives. 

The pursuit of the meaning of life is a universal human experience, and this eye represents the innate desire to find purpose and fulfilment in life.
